SUMMARY:SunHunter at the California Theatre
DESCRIPTION:High-energy acoustic alt-pop meets southern-fried grunge! SunHunter Duo rocks with heart and grit.\nSunHunter Duo brings a raw\, electrifying sound that fuses acoustic alt-pop with southern-fried grunge. Their original songs and carefully curated covers span all corners of rock\, offering something for every listener.\nWith powerhouse vocals\, gritty guitar\, and undeniable chemistry\, SunHunter delivers an unforgettable set of anthems for hopeful\, broken souls. Catch them live for a night of energy\, emotion\, and songs that stay stuck in your head long after the show ends. \nDoors Open: 6:30 PM | Show Starts: 7:30 PM\nTickets $15 in advance. $22 at door
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/sunhunter-at-the-california-theatre/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/SunHunter.jpg
