SUMMARY:Comedian Becky Robinson: The Beasts In Me Tour
DESCRIPTION:Originally from Portland\, Oregon\, Becky Robinson is an LA-based comedian\, writer\, actor\, and voice-over star who has gone from viral sensation to a sold-out theater act.\nYou may also know her as the “Entitled Housewife\,” the outspoken viral golf character Robinson created to co-star in two self-produced virtual comedy variety specials that helped spread laughter during the pandemic. Her unique character antics and viral videos have racked up millions of views across social media and garnered fans across the country (and the country clubs). In 2022\, she released the original song “Mama Needs a Claw.”
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/comedian-becky-robinson-the-beasts-in-me-tour/
LOCATION:Luther Burbank Center for the Arts\, 50 Mark West Springs Road\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Theater
