SUMMARY:Easter at the Fairgrounds
DESCRIPTION:A Full Easter Experience for the Whole Family\nJoin us for a joyful Easter celebration at the Sonoma County Fairgrounds in Santa Rosa. It’s more than a service — it’s a full family experience. Come early\, stay after\, and enjoy a relaxed\, fun atmosphere together.\nTwo Easter Services 9:00 AM & 11:00 AM\nIndoor Egg Hunts All Morning\nWhat to Expect\n• Local food trucks • Free coffee • Free family photos\nKids & Family Activities\n• Indoor Easter egg hunts throughout the morning • Bunny petting zoo • Secure kids & family areas • Friendly safety team on site\nOur indoor egg hunts happen in organized sessions so every child can enjoy the experience in a calm\, safe environment — and every child goes home with a candy bag.\nBring your family\, invite your friends\, and celebrate Easter together.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/easter-at-the-fairgrounds/
LOCATION:Sonoma County Fairgrounds\, 1350 Bennett Valley Road\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Holiday,Kids and Family,Other
GEO:38.4316;-122.704
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Sonoma County Fairgrounds 1350 Bennett Valley Road Santa Rosa CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=1350 Bennett Valley Road:geo:-122.704,38.4316
END:VEVENT
