UID:10018388-1775379600-1775401200@golocal.coop
SUMMARY:Easter Eggstravaganza at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:Annual Easter Eggstravaganza & Egg Hunt \nJoin us for our Annual Easter Eggstravaganza — free to attend and fun for the whole family. \nEgg Hunt Schedule\n10:30 AM \nAges 6 and under first \nFollowed by ages 7–9 \nThen ages 9+ \nDiorama Competition \nThis year’s theme: \nPeeps of Oz: A Wicked Tale \nPeep Launch Catapults  \nGet creative and build your own Peep-launching catapult! \nPeep Launching will happen after the egg hunt \nPast Catapults have been made form popsicle sticks\, rubberband and spoon\, cothespins\, cup and ballon….possibilities are endless!!! \nNote: No forced air devices allowed. \n  \nEaster Brunch \nServed from 9:00 AM–2:00 PM \nKids Plate — $12 \nBunny pancakes \nFruit \nEggs \nAdult Plate — $21 \nQuiche \nHam \nFresh fruit \nPastries \nBreads \nCheeses \nSpring salad \nLIVE MUSIC \nLate for the Train from 12:00–3:00 PM \nLate for the Train was born from an eclectic group of musicians who all share a love of American roots music. Part songwriter’s storybook and part jamgrass playground\, the band’s powerful live show uplifts the spirit and rouses the soul. \n  \nThis event is free to attend. Please support the business by joining us for brunch so we can continue offering this event free to the community.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/easter-eggstravaganza-at-rio-nido-roadhouse/
LOCATION:Rio Nido Roadhouse\, 14540 Canyon 2 Road\, Rio Nido\, CA
CATEGORIES:Holiday,Kids and Family,Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Peeps-3s.jpg
GEO:38.5205;-122.979
