SUMMARY:Community Easter Egg Hunt
DESCRIPTION:Join Heartwood Church for a joy-filled Easter Egg Hunt—colorful eggs\, big prizes\, sweet treats\, and fun for the whole family! \nJoin us at for a fun-filled Easter Egg Hunt celebration for the whole family! \nOur afternoon kicks off with exciting egg hunts divided by age groups\, (perfect for participants aged 0-10 years) so every child has a chance to safely and joyfully collect eggs at their own pace. Be ready for countdowns\, cheers\, and lots of smiling faces! \nIn addition to the hunts\, families can enjoy: \n-Coloring & craft tables for creative fun\n-Interactive games & activities for all ages\n-Festive photo booth to capture sweet Easter memories\n-Snacks available for purchase to keep everyone energized \nIt’s a morning full of laughter\, community\, and celebration. We can’t wait to celebrate Easter with you!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/community-easter-egg-hunt/
LOCATION:Heartwood Church\, 4689 Snyder Ln\, Rohnert Park\, CA
CATEGORIES:Holiday,Kids and Family
GEO:38.3456177;-122.6855459
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Heartwood Church 4689 Snyder Ln Rohnert Park CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=4689 Snyder Ln:geo:-122.6855459,38.3456177
