SUMMARY:ZigZag at Murphy’s
DESCRIPTION:We’re a five piece musical group based in Sonoma\, California. \nWe are a low-volume combo\, with emphasis on vocals and harmonies\, presenting a repertoire of eclectic rhythms and styles\, from jazz to latin to R and B to pop\, covering a variety of eras. \nInstrumentation is Micaelia Randolph on vocals\, David Barker on vocals and guitar\, Chuck Geber on bass\, Steve Cohen on drums\, and Scott Van Wagner on sax. \nWe have been playing regularly in various venues in Sonoma and the Bay Area.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/zigzag-at-murphys-2/
