SUMMARY:Spike Sikes and His Awesome Hotcakes at the Elephant in the Room
DESCRIPTION:The most frequently heard comment after a Spike’s Awesome Hotcakes gig goes something like this –\n“No one is making this kind of music anymore!”\nBut what\, exactly\, is “this kind of music?”\nLike hotcakes themselves\, it goes by many names. Soul. Swing. Rhythm & Blues. Jazz. Jump. It’s a sound that’s classic and simple\, but when it’s done right\, it hits the spot\, and has you grinning from ear to ear. Spike has spent years searching for this sound.\nFrom the Texas blues joints he cut his teeth in to the funky halls of New Orleans\, he was always studying the music\, trying to find just the right recipe. It makes perfect sense that he found his bandmates in Sonoma County\, a music scene that has fostered many eclectic artists for decades.\nWhat he didn’t know was how hungry audiences were for “this kind of music.” You might say they’ve been eating it up like…Hotcakes!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/spike-sikes-and-his-awesome-hotcakes-at-the-elephant-in-the-room-5/
LOCATION:Elephant in the Room\, 177A Healdsburg Avenue\, Healdsburg\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.60790;-122.86997
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Elephant in the Room 177A Healdsburg Avenue Healdsburg CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=177A Healdsburg Avenue:geo:-122.86997,38.60790
END:VEVENT
